ch.eth.scu.importer.microscopy.readers

Class BaseBioFormatsReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.eth.scu.importer.readers.AbstractReader
      • ch.eth.scu.importer.microscopy.readers.BaseBioFormatsReader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MicroscopyReader

    public abstract class BaseBioFormatsReader
extends AbstractReader
    A generic bio-formats based file processor to be specialized for the different, concrete file formats. Please mind that the BaseBioFormatsProcessor sets up all is needed to be able to parse the file, but does not parse! This is delegated to the specialized classes.
    Author:
    Aaron Ponti
